title: Black man found hanging from a tree in Los Angeles County
description: Robert L. Fuller, a 24-year-old black man, was found hanging from a tree in northern Los Angeles County. Fire department personnel who responded to the scene determined he was dead, the Los Angeles County Sheriff's Department said in a statement.

title: CNN anchor on Fox News: You can't just quote Trump lying
description: CNN's Brian Stelter compares the differences between what's happening on the ground in Seattle and how it's being covered by Fox News.

title: Tapper: Trump is standing firm with 'dead, racist losers'
description: CNN's Jake Tapper blasts President Donald Trump for refusing to rename US military bases named after Confederate leaders.
